---
layout: layouts/page.njk
title: Blog
description: Thoughts on research, tools, and machine learning.
permalink: /blog/
---

{% if collections.posts.length %}
<div class="grid grid--2">
  {% for post in collections.posts %}
  <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="card">
    <span class="card__label">{{ post.date | date("MMM yyyy") }}</span>
    <h3 class="card__title">{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
    <p class="card__text">{{ post.data.summary }}</p>
    <span class="card__link">Read &rarr;</span>
  </a>
  {% endfor %}
</div>
{% else %}
<p style="color: var(--color-text-muted);">Coming soon.</p>
{% endif %}
